| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3141 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 623f4d85-2d0e-590b-bfa1-edec8e3b170c"
